text: Sándor Réthy (15 November 1923 - 4 June 1998) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:1998 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Debrecen
